Gunmen have attacked a herdsman Alhaji Bayo and abducted his daughter in Ora-Igbomina, Osun State. The Nation gathered that the gunmen stormed the herdsman’s settlement in the Papa area of Ora-Igbomina in Ifedayo local council of the state. The incident happened on Sunday, it was learnt. Alhaji Bayo told our reporter on the phone that the gunmen came from the bush and “fired several bullets at me. I managed to escape but they entered my house and forcefully took my daughter, Memunat away through the bush they came”. Police spokesperson Yemisi Opalola confirmed the abduction.